en-US.summary: Listen to AOS Radio, less bla bla bla, more la la la.
en-US.name: AOS Radio
en-US.description:
Listen to AOS Radio, with less bla bla bla, and more la la la.

AOS Radio provides a high quality sound 24/7 with the best music.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch AOS Radio" or "Alexa, play AOS Radio" to start the radio".

At anytime, you can stop the radio by saying "Alexa, stop"
